ncil on Darfur</a>. American Rhetoric. [<a href="#identifier_5_263" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_6_263" class="footnote"><a href="http://usliberals.about.com/od/celebrityactivists/a/GClooney.htm"  class="ext-link" rel="external" target="_blank">The Politics of George Clooney, Actor and Liberal Political Activist</a>. Usliberals. Retrieved 2/24/12 [<a href="#identifier_6_263" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li></ol><div class='yarpp-related'>
